### Summary
Prior to 2010, I was a fashion designer for 14 years. I've worked in women's, men's and children's wear, for global labels to smaller couture labels. I've also made many dresses for special occasions -- wedding and evening dresses. I specialized in custom corseted strapless dresses with boning. And while I haven't done any fashion design recently, I've found ways of incorporating aspects of it into my games in the form of wearable game controllers. 

